  "description_short": "Institutional-grade financial data API with real-time WebSocket streaming, tick-level data, and broad market coverage.",
  "description_long": "Polygon.io provides institutional-grade financial data through a modern REST and WebSocket API, covering stocks, options, forex, and crypto markets. The platform is known for its low-latency real-time data, tick-level historical data, and comprehensive market coverage.\n\nUnlike Alpha Vantage which focuses on simplicity, Polygon.io targets more demanding use cases with WebSocket streaming for real-time data, millisecond-precision timestamps, and aggregated bar data from 1-second to daily intervals. The API also provides reference data, corporate actions, financial statements, and SEC filings.\n\nThe free tier is more generous than most competitors at 5 API requests per minute with delayed data. Paid plans start at $199/month for real-time data access, making it a serious investment but one that provides genuinely institutional-quality data feeds.",
